title: (x) Roti Shop script - Jukebox Stephanie Marie {Alejandro Paul}
content:
Hi All,

I’m looking for the script font that appears in this image. I’ve been told it was called “eebie” but a web search doesn’t reveal any links and I’m starting to think it must be called something else.

Any help is greatly appreciated.

 ![](http://web.archive.org/files/home_welcome_4751.jpg)
author: khayden
